MESSAGE: When the attribute “xml:lang” in no namespace is specified, the element must also have the attribute “lang” present with the same value.
Internal encoding declaration “iso-8859-1” disagrees with the actual encoding of the document (“utf-8”).

FIRSTLINE: charset=iso-8859-1” for attribute “content” on element “meta”: “iso-8859-1” is not a preferred encoding name. The preferred label for this encoding is “windows-1252”.
